data.description: *Morrison Lake* 1.28 Acre Lakefront Home with Pole barn!!  Properties like this are very hard to come by on the water!  3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, large covered patio with gas line for that outdoor kitchen, 90 ft. aluminum dock, upper bonus/game room with its own mini split, open concept kitchen with corian countertops, living, and dining room, extra family/rec room. Updated bathrooms, 2 car attached garage, underground lawn sprinkler system.  30x40 Pole barn, park like setting with a long driveway for plenty of parking in a well maintained neighborhood.  Storage galore above Garage with shelving, as well as above covered patio.This Place has it all.  Call today for your private showing! This company makes no warranty or representations about the contents of this data including room sizes & sq. footage. It is the responsibility of the parties looking at the property to satisfy themselves as to the accuracy of this information. Taxes were obtained from the local assessor and the taxes could change for the buyer after a closed transaction.
